examples.en: I don't like highly spiced dishes.
Nursing is a highly skilled job.
His services are perhaps too highly paid.
Man is a highly intelligent animal.
Her co-workers spoke highly of her.
Photosynthesis is a highly complex process.
She is a highly educated woman.
She is highly qualified for the job.
He is highly regarded as a mechanic.
He made some highly critical remarks.
The car has a highly original design.
